  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to compare the efficacy of high frequency (HF SCS) stimulation and
      sham stimulation (Sham SCS - i.e. no stimulation) and conventional spinal cord stimulation
      (Conv SCS) on the patient reported global impression of change, pain intensity and health
      related quality of life.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
